- But there is some form of fire combat, termite, e.g.

64
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:54,760
It is extremely warm fragments. It gives the fireworks -like effects.

65
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:58,680
They have the ability to burn through even buildings-

66
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:01.560
–And causes very severe burns to humans.

67
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:05.040
It is war crime to use such indiscriminately.

68
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:08,760
Why does Russia use this type of bombs?

69
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:13,200
It's a way to beat over a fairly large territory -

70
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:17,480
- When the Ukrainian defenders are in the city of Bachmut where they are fortified.

71
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:20,200
You do not know exactly where they are.

72
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:24,880
But you can use such to knock out people in buildings.

73
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:33,040
Over 1,500 armored vehicles and 230 tanks

74
