has been delivered to Ukraine's counter -offensive.

75
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:41,800
According to the Financial Times, 35,000 Ukrainian soldiers are ready to attack.

76
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:48,200
If we take the Russian -cooked area - what could a counter -offensive look like?

77
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:54,400
The most important thing about a counter -offensive is that it also generates a political victory -

78
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57.560
- As the Russian leadership in Moscow affects.

79
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:03,160
What could really do it is an attack in this part -

80
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:07.640
– There Ukraine would attack towards Melitopol -

81
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:12,200
–To cut off the railway connection in particular down towards the Crimea -

82
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,720
- As you depend on for logistics.

83
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:18,080
Russia, then, what does their line of defense look like?

84
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:22,880
Since October, Russia has actually dug several layers in stock -

85
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:26,880
–A of minefields, shooting boars and tanks -

86
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:30,480
- To make the Ukrainian offensive more difficult.

87
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:33,600
You may not stop it, but you buy time -

88
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:39,240
- For Russian reinforcements that may come where Ukraine breaks through.

89
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:43,520
Here it is also important to remember that the Ukrainian counter -offensive -

90
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:47,680
- Can be several counter -offensives who see where you break through.

91
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:51,840
If you break through in one direction you can continue there towards different goals.

92
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:59,640
But most important is to break the supply that goes all the way to Crimea.

93
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:03,200
- The railway then? -Yes exactly.

94
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:06,720
When does the counter -offensive come, then?

95
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09.120
To some extent, it has almost already begun.

96
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:12,520
Ukraine has started some minor attacks.

97
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:19,200
Then maybe you can see that it really starts when the tanks come.

98
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:22,600
But in principle, the Ukrainian forces are ready.

99
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:27,120
The last clay will disappear within one to two weeks-

100
